  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients currently receiving hemodialysis will be randomized to receive 1 of 3 dialysate
      sodium prescriptions. The effects on blood pressure, interdialytic weight gain, thirst, and
      intradialytic symptoms will be assessed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
